{"tid":411504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飯店枕頭裡有「刺蝟」　女孩一坐「屁股開花」血噴整床","createTime":"2017-09-24T00:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T09:30:42.000Z","uid":100136,"like":63,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d11edfab628d3be37ca450b50b72040e6bd9268","tid":411504,"uid":100136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T00:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/084026_24b16a573aa445a988c02dc305e192cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F084026_24b16a573aa445a988c02dc305e192cd.jpg&h=2d190afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n陝西西安市一間飯店深夜傳出一聲尖叫，一名女房客人狂奔而出，屁股被刺出了一堆洞，還流出大量鮮血！同房的親友查看後才發現，女房客剛才一屁股坐下去的枕頭內，竟藏著一隻全身是刺的「小刺蝟」。<br />\n<br />\n女房客的親友李姓男子表示，他們一行4人20日上午入住長安區的「旺角飯店」，晚上回房以後，看見枕頭上有一點髒污，但沒有想太多，後來準備休息時，女房客躺在枕頭上，突然驚呼了一聲，屁股流出了大量鮮血，「床單上都是血，我們想枕頭裡面可能藏東西，馬上打開來看，結果竟然是一隻刺蝟！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/084043_3d3db4d52e7372726169e170217d5ba8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F084043_3d3db4d52e7372726169e170217d5ba8.jpg&h=e033cb7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲飯店枕頭裡有「刺蝟」　女孩一坐「屁股開花啦」血噴床單。（圖／都市快報）<br />\n<br />\n李男一行人當下馬上找飯店老闆理論，但對方卻不承認，還堅持房間很乾淨，「房間天天都打掃，衛生沒有問題，而且上午他們都沒事，現在突然就說有刺蝟？」雙方越說越僵，最後竟然打了起來，把房間弄得一團亂，直到警方到場後才停手。<br />\n<br />\n由於雙方各說各話，完全沒有共識，因此目前警方還在調查刺蝟到底從何而來。<br />\n<br />\n▼刺蝟還活著，但沒人知道他怎麼出現的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/084100_7e37e3f29021cb0cb1e60e17d97bdc50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F084100_7e37e3f29021cb0cb1e60e17d97bdc50.jpg&h=8e7377e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲飯店枕頭裡有「刺蝟」　女孩一坐「屁股開花啦」血噴床單。（圖／都市快報）<br />\n<br />\n▼警方到場後，房客跟老闆才停止互毆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/084147_830a04ce9b1a243f581387c076aa5739.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F084147_830a04ce9b1a243f581387c076aa5739.jpg&h=4d2a5b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源: <a href=\"https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1017027?from=fb_et_pets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpets.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1017027%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_pets&d=hUUeBhi%2FZbZ2J%2Bxlb%2FwNl10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e223904f\" target=\"_blank\">https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1017027?from=fb_et_pets</a>"},{"pid":"04b7cd5aea6a07603f1dda0cdc86487d161bb653","tid":411504,"uid":51388,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"刺蝟RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98aa05095e8c6cf39ed79609f3b208f329030d94","tid":411504,"uid":100136,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T00:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>刺蝟RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲未死㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a83847fa6680ef952a4922f5f677b434451b6c3","tid":411504,"uid":44512,"like":225,"dislike":6,"score":219,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T00:46:44.000Z","msg":"刺蝟bb 表示： 黑人問號.jpg"},{"pid":"881396cf085251cec0b535a75895aefef9ebde4f","tid":411504,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T00:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989e8fa5fb106470593f2c6554b4c4f4040c8652","tid":411504,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T00:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚堅"},{"pid":"3ed78031010445c5918b4f9ded6f8f09960c0ef5","tid":411504,"uid":32527,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T00:51:38.000Z","msg":"見到血都覺得痛"},{"pid":"d4747ad02d46d6e5387355e5b2990a7a95eda553","tid":411504,"uid":100136,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score